    "text": "Question 2\n\ncl&lt;- makeCluster(4)\nregisterDoParallel(cl)\n\n#Set no of Bootstrapping samples\nB&lt;- 1000\n\n#Parallel bootsrapping\nsystem.time(result2&lt;- foreach(i=1:B,combine=rbind,.packages = 'MASS')%dopar%{\n  \n  median(sample(galaxies,replace =TRUE))\n})\n\n   user  system elapsed \n   0.18    0.04    0.31 \n\nstopCluster(cl)\n\n#Serial bootstrapping for comparison \nsystem.time(result2&lt;- foreach(i=1:B,combine=c,.packages = 'MASS')%do%{\n  \n  median(sample(galaxies,replace =T))\n})\n\n   user  system elapsed \n   0.16    0.00    0.17"
  },
  {
    "objectID": "Assignment2.html#question-3",
    "href": "Assignment2.html#question-3",
    "title": "Assignment2",
    "section": "Question 3",
    "text": "Question 3\n\nset.seed(1234)\n\ntsamples&lt;- rexp(n=50,rate=1)\n\ntruemean&lt;- 1\n\nB&lt;- 1000\n\ncover&lt;-0 #No of confidence intervals\n  \nfor(i in 1:1000)\n  {\n  sampled&lt;- rexp(50,1)\n  \n \n  bootmean&lt;- function(data, indices) {       #Bootstrap samples\n    return(mean(data[indices]))\n }\n\n  bootres &lt;- boot(sampled,bootmean,R=B)\n  \n  \n  #percentile bootsrap\n  cint&lt;- boot.ci(bootres,type=\"perc\")$percent[4:5]\n  \n  if (!is.null(cint) && truemean &gt;= cint[1] && truemean &lt;= cint[2]) {\n    cover &lt;- cover + 1\n    \n  }\n  \n}\n\n#Estimated coverage probability\n\ncov.prob&lt;- cover/1000 \n\ncov.prob\n\n[1] 0.929"
  },
